arStrings.szText: Let the Light push out the darkness hiding within this woman! Father, force this demon out!
Solemn. You are conducting a magic ritual and the words are important to get right. Said with conviction.
¡Que la luz destierre la oscuridad que se oculta en esta mujer! Padre, ¡expulsa este demonio!
